import React from 'react' import './About.css' const About = () => { return ( <>

What I am Expert In

Transforming Electrical Concepts into
Real-world Solutions.

Electrical Engineering

I am a dedicated student specializing in Power and Electrical Machines Engineering at Beirut Arab University, with an anticipated graduation year of 2026. Throughout my academic journey, I have developed a profound understanding of electrical systems, power generation, and machine design. My coursework, combined with practical experiences, has equipped me with the skills to innovate and optimize electrical solutions for various applications.

This portfolio showcases my academic projects, research, and professional experiences that illustrate my competencies in the field of electrical engineering. My work demonstrates a commitment to advancing technology and contributing to sustainable energy solutions.

Please feel free to explore my projects and reach out with any questions or collaboration opportunities.
